	* alpha/README.alpha, alpha/udi_abi.h: udi_index_t is 8 bits; 
	udi_size_t is 64 bits on 64-bit hosts.
	* ia32/README.ia32, ia32/udi_abi.h: Likewise.
	* ia64/README.ia32, ia64/udi_abi.h: Likewise.
	* ppc/README.ia32, ppc/udi_abi.h: Likewise.
	* sparc/README.ia32, sparc/udi_abi.h: Likewise.
